OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1779883867
OL,3,CWoman dies after shooting in Sheffield
OL,4,Ccity centre
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after a woman was shot in
OL,8,FSheffield.
OL,10,FSouth Yorkshire Police were called to
OL,11,FWest Street, outside the One Four One
OL,12,Fbar, at 2.45am on Monday 25 May.
OL,14,FOfficers found evidence "consistent
OL,15,Fwith a firearms discharge".
OL,17,FThe 30-year-old woman was found with
OL,18,Fserious injuries. She was treated at
OL,19,Fthe scene before being taken to
OL,20,Fhospital, where she later died.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
