PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1779883867
OL,3,CWoman dies after shooting in Sheffield
OL,4,Ccity centre
OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable, Colin
OL,7,FMcFarlane, said: "This is a
OL,8,Fdevastating incident which has
OL,9,Fresulted in the death of a young woman
OL,10,Fwhile on a night out during the bank
OL,11,Fholiday weekend in Sheffield.
OL,13,F"First and foremost, our thoughts are
OL,14,Fwith her family and everyone who knew
OL,15,Fand loved her.
OL,17,F"Three people have been arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
