OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1779883867
OL,3,CWoman dies after shooting in Sheffield
OL,4,Ccity centre
OL,6,F"Our officers have been working
OL,7,Fextremely hard to piece together the
OL,8,Fevents surrounding the shooting. While
OL,9,Four investigation is in its early
OL,10,Fstages, we will continue to have a
OL,11,Fsignificant presence at the scene in
OL,12,Fthe area today and in the coming days.
OL,14,F"Bank holidays are one of the busiest
OL,15,Ftimes of the year, and we know that
OL,16,Fthere were people in the area around
OL,17,FWest Street and Eldon Street who saw
OL,18,Fwhat happened or know who is
OL,19,Fresponsible.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
